text: Tansterne is a hamlet in the East Riding of Yorkshire, England. It is situated approximately north-east of Sproatley and south-west of Aldbrough. It lies off the B1238 road. Tansterne Grange It forms part of the civil parish of Aldbrough. ==References== * ==External links== * Category:Villages in the East Riding of Yorkshire Category:Holderness
